%% Diagram: Diagram 4
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as API
    participant F as Fraud
    participant P as Processor
    participant N as Network
    participant I as Bank
    participant L as Ledger

    C->>API: POST /payments
    API->>API: Idempotency check
    API->>F: Score txn
    F->>API: allow (risk 25)
    API->>P: PaymentIntent
    P->>N: Authorize
    N->>I: Verify funds
    I->>N: Approved
    N->>P: Auth ok
    P->>API: Authorized
    API->>L: Record auth
    API->>C: 201 authorized

    Note over C,L: Later: Capture

    C->>API: POST /capture
    API->>P: Capture
    P->>N: Capture
    N->>API: Captured
    API->>L: Record capture
    API->>C: 200 captured

    Note over C,L: T+2: Settlement

    P-->>API: Webhook payout
    API->>L: Record settlement
